title: Gordon wins batting title, but Marlins fall to Phillies 7-2
text:
> Florida Gordon wins batting title, but Marlins fall to Phillies 7-2 Miami Marlins' Dee Gordon (9) is congratulated in the dugout by teammates after scoring on a double by Justin Bour in the first inning against the Philadelphia Phillies during a baseball game Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015, in Philadelphia. (AP Photo/Rich Schultz)
